You are helping develop "나아포" (Naapo), a pain tracking mobile app for a Korean university software contest (NE:XT Contest, Korea University).

## Project Overview
- App name: 나아포
- Mascots: 라포 (seahorse, recording chatbot), 아포 (dolphin, medical consultation chatbot)
- Concept: Ocean theme, blue color palette, user-friendly UI

## Tech Stack
- React Native + Expo (TypeScript)
- Supabase (auth + database)
- Claude API (for 라포 and 아포 chatbots)
- expo-router (file-based navigation)
- react-native-calendars (heatmap calendar)
- Victory Native (charts/reports)
- react-native-svg (body map)

## Navigation Structure
Bottom tabs: 홈 (Home) / 라포 (Record chatbot) / 아포 (Medical chatbot)
Stack navigator on top of tabs for detail screens.

## Database Tables (Supabase)
- users: id, nickname, coins, selected_character, created_at
- pain_records: id, user_id, body_part, intensity(0-10), pain_type[], sleep_hours, emotion, daily_note, recorded_at
- prescriptions: id, user_id, diagnosis, medicine_name, dosage_rule, start_date, created_at

## Key Features
- 라포 chatbot: conversational pain recording (body map touch, intensity 0-10 slider, pain type tags, sleep/emotion/daily notes) → 10 coins per record
- 아포 chatbot: free-form medical consultation using Claude API
- Home screen: heatmap calendar (C), stats cards (most frequent pain D, avg intensity E, count F), health magazine banner (B), profile character (A)
- Report (G): pain pattern analysis, trigger correlation analysis
- Prescription management (H): diagnosis, medicine, dosage rules
- Gamification: coins system, character unlock (500 coins per character)

## Coding Rules
- Always use TypeScript
- All UI text in Korean
- Use functional components with hooks
- Keep components small and reusable
- Store Supabase keys in .env file (never hardcode)
- Follow ocean/blue theme consistently
- Comment complex logic in Korean

## Color Palette (Ocean Theme)
- Primary: #4A90D9 (ocean blue)
- Secondary: #7EC8E3 (light blue)
- Background: #F0F8FF (alice blue)
- Accent: #2E5FA3 (deep blue)
- Text: #1A2E4A (dark navy)
